Package: medmodr
Title: Mediation and Moderation Modeling Utilities for R
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person(given = "Tosin Harold", family = "Akingbemisilu", email = "tosinakingbemisilu@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"), comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-0556-9955"))
Description: Provides utilities to fit, summarize, visualize, and iterate mediation and moderation analyses, enabling users to efficiently scan multiple predictors, mediators, moderators, and outcomes within tidy workflows.
